+       t=0     backdrop dim fades in:   bg 0→0.5 alpha   (modalBackdropIn)
+       t=0.10  dialog-full white panel fades in: opacity 0→1   (dialogFullFade)
+       t=0.35  close button              (contentIn, translateY 10→0 + fade)
+       t=0.40  dialog-head (title + h3) (contentIn)
+       t=0.50  results-privacy banner   (contentIn)
+       t=0.60  dialog-lead paragraph    (contentIn)
+       t=0.70+ card grid flips in        (cardFlipDown, 50ms stagger × 12)
+       t≈1.80  results-request fades in
