+     Each step uses keyframe animations with backwards fill so the
+     pre-animation state (0% keyframe) is applied during the delay
+     window. Once an animation ends, the cascade falls back to the
+     visible state defined inside the `.modal.open` selector — keeping
+     elements visible AND leaving their transforms free for hover.
