+       through the section's full height; vertical scroll progress is
+       converted into a horizontal card advance — when the section is
+       fully visible, the page appears to "stop" and the cards inside
+       cycle one by one; once all 5 cards have been seen, the sticky
+       releases and the page resumes scrolling to Section 4.
+       Left rail: vertical tabs (each tab text = card title). Right:
+       horizontal track of 5 stacked cards, each filling the right
+       column; adjacent cards bleed off the section edges (clipped).
+       Tabs are clickable too — click jumps to the matching scroll
+       position so users who don't want to scroll can still navigate.
