+.cta-pair, .stage-actions, .modal-actions {
+  flex-direction: column;
+  align-items: stretch;
+  width: 100%;
+  max-width: 360px;
+  gap: 10px;
+}
+.cta-pair > .btn-primary,
+.cta-pair > .btn-ghost {
+  width: 100%;
+  justify-content: center;
+  min-height: 44px;
+}
+```
+
+同款 idiom 已用在：
+- Sticky bottom CTA bar
